flowchart TD
    %% Data Source Node
    A[Salary Dataset CSV]:::dataSource --> B[DataFrame 'data']:::dataVariable

    %% DataFrame to Feature/Target Nodes
    B --> C[Features 'x']:::dataVariable
    B --> D[Target 'y']:::dataVariable

    %% Splitting Data
    C & D --> E[train_test_split]:::process
    E --> F[xtrain, xtest, ytrain, ytest]:::dataVariable

    %% ML Model Creation
    F --> G[Linear Regression Model 'L']:::model
    G --> H[L.fit(xtrain, ytrain)]:::process

    %% Prediction Node
    H --> I[y_pred = L.predict(xtest)]:::dataVariable

    %% Data Nodes Styles
    classDef dataVariable fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef dataSource fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;
